    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25136944_14_1041-1113",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "1041-1113",
      "markText": "那时我还不了解人性有多么矛盾，我不知道真诚的表现中含有多少演戏的成分，高尚的品行中又隐藏着多少卑鄙的动机，或者反过来说，恶行的背后是否也有善意？",
      "totalCount": 1365,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25136944&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1041&rangeEnd=1113",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/34e323e0717f8f3034ee3cc?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1041&rangeEnd=1113"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25136944_7_3852-3915",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3852-3915",
      "markText": "“为什么好女人总是嫁给无趣的男人？” “因为有脑子的男人不娶好女人。”",
      "totalCount": 1326,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25136944&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3852&rangeEnd=3915",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/34e323e0717f8f3034ee3cc?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3852&rangeEnd=3915"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25136944_18_5343-5422",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "5343-5422",
      "markText": "女人往往特别喜欢在她们所爱的人临终时表现得格外宽宏大量，这种喜好总是令人感到惶恐不安。有时我甚至觉得她们不愿意男人寿命太长，害得她们迟迟没有机会演出这幕好戏。",
      "totalCount": 1140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25136944&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=5343&rangeEnd=5422",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/34e323e0717f8f3034ee3cc?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=5343&rangeEnd=5422"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25136944_20_2100-2134",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "2100-2134",
      "markText": "幸福有时会成就高尚的品性，而苦难往往只会让人变得心胸狭窄，报复心强。",
      "totalCount": 1090,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25136944&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2100&rangeEnd=2134",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/34e323e0717f8f3034ee3cc?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2100&rangeEnd=2134"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25136944_24_4411-4432",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "4411-4432",
      "markText": "“我不想过去。只有永恒的现在才是重要的。”",
      "totalCount": 1071,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25136944&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=4411&rangeEnd=4432",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/34e323e0717f8f3034ee3cc?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=4411&rangeEnd=4432"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25136944_20_840-913",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "840-913",
      "markText": "我们每天的生活就像有轨电车沿着轨道从起点站到终点站往返行驶，有多少乘客上了我们的车也大概能数得过来。生活被安排得太井然有序了。这让我感到心惊胆战。",
      "totalCount": 935,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25136944&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=840&rangeEnd=913",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/34e323e0717f8f3034ee3cc?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=840&rangeEnd=913"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25136944_44_3993-4035",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "3993-4035",
      "markText": "“一个女人可以原谅男人对她的伤害，”他说，“但是永远不能原谅男人为了她而做出牺牲。”",
      "totalCount": 890,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25136944&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=3993&rangeEnd=4035",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/34e323e0717f8f3034ee3cc?chapterUid=44&rangeStart=3993&rangeEnd=4035"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25136944_5_2875-2913",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2875-2913",
      "markText": "如果我写作不是只为了自娱自乐，还抱有什么其他目的，那我就是个傻瓜中的傻瓜了。",
      "totalCount": 868,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25136944&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2875&rangeEnd=2913",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/34e323e0717f8f3034ee3cc?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2875&rangeEnd=2913"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25136944_7_1314-1361",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1314-1361",
      "markText": "她心里鄙视世人追逐名流的弱点，却仍能不失热情地跟他们周旋应酬，表现出一个名流女作家的大度气派。",
      "totalCount": 816,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25136944&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1314&rangeEnd=1361",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/34e323e0717f8f3034ee3cc?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1314&rangeEnd=1361"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25136944_4_2327-2353",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2327-2353",
      "markText": "艺术是表现情感的，而表现情感的语言是人人都能理解的。",
